PN,44601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FFuel trucks have regained access to an
OL,8,Foil refinery that had been subjected
OL,9,Fto a days-long blockade after Irish
OL,10,Fpolice cleared protesters from the
OL,11,Fentrance.
OL,13,FIn a major operation involving scores
OL,14,Fof gardai, large tractors that had
OL,15,Fbeen blocking the entrance to the
OL,16,FWhitegate oil refinery in Co Cork were
OL,17,Fmoved and fuel tankers were once again
OL,18,Fable to access the site.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThe operation to secure the site took
OL,8,Fapproximately an hour and saw some
OL,9,Fphysical clashes between the Public
OL,10,FOrder Unit and protesters, including
OL,11,Finstances where pepper spray was used.
OL,13,FMembers of the Defence Forces were
OL,14,Falso at the scene as the Irish police
OL,15,Fservice, An Garda Siochana, had
OL,16,Frequested the availability of a
OL,17,Fmilitary heavy-lift recovery truck if
OL,18,Fit needed to tow any of the large
OL,19,Ftractors or trucks involved in the
OL,20,Fblockade.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FGardai escorted the fuel trucks to the
OL,8,Fpremises.
OL,10,FAn Garda Siochana had internally
OL,11,Fdeclared an "exceptional event",
OL,12,Fenabling the large-scale response by
OL,13,Fallowing it to designate every member
OL,14,Fas available for duty over the weekend.
OL,26,@sD@MOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThe reopening of Whitegate will
OL,8,Falleviate some concerns about the
OL,9,Fcountry's filling stations running
OL,10,Fcompletely dry after days of blockades
OL,11,Fat the Cork facility, as well as
OL,12,Fdepots in Limerick and Galway,
OL,13,Fstrangled the fuel distribution
OL,14,Fnetwork.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThe blockades are part of nationwide
OL,8,Fprotests by hauliers, farmers and
OL,9,Fagricultural contractors who are
OL,10,Furging the Government to take action
OL,11,Fto reduce fuel costs which they say
OL,12,Fare at unsustainable levels and will
OL,13,Flead to people going out of business.
OL,15,FThe protests have also seen slow-
OL,16,Fmoving convoys and outright stoppages
OL,17,Fon the motorway network as well as the
OL,18,Festablishment of a large blockade on
OL,19,FDublin city's main thoroughfare,
OL,20,FO'Connell Street.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Government ministers re-
OL,8,Fentered talks with established
OL,9,Frepresentative organisations for the
OL,10,Ftransport and agricultural sectors
OL,11,Faimed at defusing the protests.
OL,13,FThe recognised bodies in the meetings
OL,14,Fare not responsible for organising the
OL,15,Fdistinct protests around the country
OL,16,Fbut are also working to secure
OL,17,Freductions in operating costs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FProtesters had sought their own
OL,8,Fengagements with Government and
OL,9,Fexpressed anger at being excluded from
OL,10,Fthe talks.
OL,12,FThe development at Whitegate came
OL,13,Fafter Fuels for Ireland chief
OL,14,Fexecutive Kevin McPartlan said around
OL,15,F600 of the 1,500 filling stations
OL,16,Faround the Republic of Ireland had run
OL,17,Fdry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FHe had predicted that the number
OL,8,F"would grow quite dramatically" if the
OL,9,Fblockades on Whitegate, Galway and
OL,10,FFoynes, Co Limerick, continued.
OL,12,FElsewhere, Rosslare Europort is
OL,13,Fexpected to hit capacity by Sunday
OL,14,Fevening or Monday morning.
OL,16,FOperations at the port, run by Irish
OL,17,FRail, have been affected by a blockade
OL,18,Fof fuel protesters in the nearby town
OL,19,Fof Kilrane, Co Wexford.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Irish Rail said the
OL,8,Fport will soon be at capacity and will
OL,9,Fnot be able to take in any more
OL,10,Ffreight ` resulting in ships having to
OL,11,Fwait on anchor or be diverted to
OL,12,Fanother port if possible.
OL,14,FBlockades have resulted in full
OL,15,Fclosures of parts of the M50 ring road
OL,16,Faround Dublin, as well as the M4, M6,
OL,17,FM7, M8, M9 and M20.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FTransport Infrastructure Ireland,
OL,8,Fwhich is responsible for motorways,
OL,9,Fsaid there is "significant disruption"
OL,10,Fto its network affecting counties
OL,11,FClare, Limerick, Tipperary, Laois,
OL,12,FOffaly, Kildare, Galway, Cork, and
OL,13,FDublin.
OL,15,FIt said it was working closely with
OL,16,Fgardai in managing traffic
OL,17,Fdistribution.
OL,26,@qD@OOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
