OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThe protests have caused disruption to
OL,8,Fsome bus routes across Ireland and
OL,9,Fwithin the capital, where Luas Green
OL,10,FLine tram services are also affected.
OL,12,FParticipants say the Government needs
OL,13,Fto take urgent action on fuel prices
OL,14,For they will go out of business.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThere have also been concerns about
OL,8,Ffuel shortages leading to the
OL,9,Fcurtailment of emergency services and
OL,10,Fthe delivery of vital goods, while the
OL,11,FNational Emergency Coordination Group
OL,12,Furged people to only buy the fuel they
OL,13,Fneed.
OL,15,FHealth Minister Jennifer Carroll
OL,16,FMacNeill told the Irish Medical
OL,17,FOrganisation AGM in Co Kerry on
OL,18,FSaturday that "all of our ambulances
OL,19,Fhave been refuelled successfully".
OL,26,@zD@OOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin warned that
OL,8,FIreland is on the "precipice of
OL,9,Fturning oil away from the country",
OL,10,Fdescribing the situation as
OL,11,F"unconscionable", "illogical", and
OL,12,F"difficult to comprehend".
OL,14,FA commitment from the coalition on
OL,15,FFriday night to deliver a
OL,16,F"substantial" package of measures on
OL,17,Ffuel costs was not enough to dissuade
OL,18,Fprotesters from continuing blockades.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@bO]sD@AOUsD@PO]sD@SOUsD@]O]tD@
OL,26,AAOUtD@YO]xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
