OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FChristopher Duffy, a spokesman for the
OL,8,Fgrouping in Dublin city centre, said
OL,9,Fthe protest would continue until there
OL,10,Fwas a "serious reduction in our costs".
OL,12,FTalks between Government departments
OL,13,Fand representative bodies reopened at
OL,14,Flunchtime on Saturday, with a view to
OL,15,Ffinalising what deputy premier Simon
OL,16,FHarris said would be "substantial and
OL,17,Fsignificant" measures for affected
OL,18,Findustries.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@fO]xD@VOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThe president of the Irish Road
OL,8,FHaulage Association, which is not
OL,9,Forganising the protests, said he was
OL,10,F"hopeful" that there would be a
OL,11,Fresolution by Saturday evening.
OL,13,FSpeaking before a meeting at the
OL,14,FDepartment of Transport, Ger Hyland
OL,15,Fsaid: "Certainly nobody is going to
OL,16,Fget everything what we want ` we put a
OL,17,Fraft of proposals to Government last
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@IO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
