PN,44616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775981091
OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,F"That's what we're coming in to
OL,8,Fnegotiate on today. We're coming in
OL,9,Fwith an open mind, there's no red
OL,10,Flines."
OL,12,FPolice in Northern Ireland said they
OL,13,Fwere "maintaining an ongoing
OL,14,Fassessment" in relation to social
OL,15,Fmedia posts calling for similar
OL,16,Fplanned protests there.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@GO]uD@FOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
