OL,3,CFuel tankers regain access to Irish
OL,4,Coil refinery after Garda clear
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FA PSNI spokeswoman said: "A policing
OL,8,Fresponse has been prepared, if needed,
OL,9,Fto ensure public safety and to help
OL,10,Fminimise any potential disruption to
OL,11,Fthe wider community."
